<paragraph id="CE33295C37515170FE78B1BA39C4A445" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Tonzigs Leinkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="6D7AFAD7F365C7877BC13E948688ACF8" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" type="description">
<paragraph id="4F8AA23202F3CFFDF770FA18B70D5190" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="AE9EB59FB381143276426D6F8168B388" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="94A912DA10E07AF2372485683F501DD0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<authorityName id="FB9A277D9DD55F1489121A698B6E84C2" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">L.</authorityName>
alpina
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 11) durch folgende Merkmale: Bis 12 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="4E71E6F4483E2368A3A6384C794ABD4F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
unterirdisch im 
<normalizedToken id="BEA8CE30131EE5C582542662CFD31A6F" originalValue="Geröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Geroell</normalizedToken>
kriechend; Stengel bogig auf steigend; 
<normalizedToken id="2476777F065C9F88F9A2361FD7E93024" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
lanzettlich, 1
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="8BFA6B1D711ED5E71CE3ED3A618253A2" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">1/2</normalizedToken>
- 
<emphasis id="245E0B78710E18C4924236319B3F1078" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
3mal so lang wie breit; 
<normalizedToken id="016CB635FDEBF305A229E085399332B8" originalValue="Blütenstiel" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Bluetenstiel</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="0333755A6E319B91A644E02633CA368A" originalValue="höchstens" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">hoechstens</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="42B1E64D86D3AA6FFBB669D60E9CE5A3" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="95A64E7BAD3051AFC343407C450EAB80" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">so lang wie der Kelch, wie der untere Teil des Kelches zottig behaart</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="16F52FCEBFD41E1E897C45BAE1D6B177" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Haare mehrzellig, 0,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="244B11586FAA0FE86836A632C48423EC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">2 mm lang</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="ECEB9ACFB0A9EF9E51D1C8525F181A39" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">;</emphasis>
Kelch mit ovalen bis lanzettlichen Abschnitten; Krone 1,2-1,8 cm lang (ohne Sporn), 
<emphasis id="80C793C0FE2A205EFE257A96F1DC7B26" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">gelb</emphasis>
, Zipfel der Oberlippe kaum 
<normalizedToken id="4A5BD197BC68D3F76013BC8F6C9DDFF6" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">laenger</normalizedToken>
als breit. - 
<normalizedToken id="00ECA1E2F5E97257A20AE42F2596E862" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6C15C87510B6399D670BCF1487AFAA17" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="C4D3BB3FDCB6988F74F045DBB2EBE684" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1B6A600D89908963FC06B5BECB137A03" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="ECE53283A7DF3F0C6740EAFD5A0B07C7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Bewegliches 
<normalizedToken id="FE0662FE56A4CB77FF9484CDBC563DFD" originalValue="Kalkgeröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Kalkgeroell</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A4D7313E233C017BB44171DF07B32E1B" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="E54E7FEEEF47B957090EE2B23CE81D47" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Verbreitung. Bergamasker Pflanze:</emphasis>
Pizzo Arera (Fenaroli 1954), Cima di Menna, Monte Pegherolo (Kunz und Reichstein 1959).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
